              <h3>The PRIMIS Asthma audit tool live demonstration</h3>
              <p>16<sup>th</sup> July 2015 at 12.30-13.15</p>
              <p>Join Lauren Fensome from PRIMIS as she gives an introduction to the PRIMIS asthma care audit tool, after which she will give a live demonstration on how to use the tool to the webinar attendees. This webinar will follow-on from the previous webinar in the series by Dr Mark Levy and Dan Murphy, addressing National Review of Asthma Deaths (NRAD) 2014 and the unmet need for treatments. This demonstration will also run through particular filters or searches relevant to clinical practice. This webinar will provide practical insight on the tool in order to help practices optimise management and care of patients.</p>
              <br />
              <p><%= link_to "Live Webcast", live_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
              <%= link_to "Archived Webcast", archive_path, class: "btn btn-danger" %></p>
